summary: This document is a closing report from the Metropolitan Police Service regarding a request for assistance from US authorities in a human trafficking and perjury investigation. It details the request for a birth certificate of a witness named Anouska Guest and confirms that all lines of inquiry have been completed.

persons.name: Anouska Guest
persons.context: Anouska Guest is mentioned as a witness in the context of a human trafficking and perjury investigation, with a request made for her birth certificate.

persons.name: Detective Constable
persons.context: The Detective Constable from the Metropolitan Police International Assistance Unit is responsible for the closing report and communication with US authorities.

keyFacts: The US authorities requested assistance from the UK regarding a human trafficking and perjury investigation.
The UK authorities were asked to obtain a copy of the birth certificate of a witness named Anouska Guest.
Anouska Guest was born in Ascot, England.
The inquiry has been marked as complete by the International Assistance Unit of the Metropolitan Police.
The document is subject to a protective order, indicating sensitive information.
